  "text": "Epicardial coronary artery stenosis has a clinical impact on HD patients. In addition, coronary microcirculatory impairment has been an important issue in HD patients [CITATION_1] . In such situations, specific medical treatment such as nicorandil may have beneficial effects on improving coronary microcirculatory flow, resulting in better clinical prognosis in the HD population [CITATION_2] .",
